    <item>
      <title>随着火灾担忧加剧，加州允许将再保险成本计入保费</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/california-allows-reinsurance-cost-in-rates-as-fire-worry-grows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加州批准了新规定，允许保险公司在制定费率时考虑再保险成本，这是监管改革的最后一项重要举措，旨在阻止在人们对野火的担忧日益加剧之际保险公司大批撤离。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/california-allows-reinsurance-cost-in-rates-as-fire-worry-grows</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 21:54:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新兴市场资产因全球情绪低落、交易清淡而下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/turkish-lira-slips-on-erdogan-rates-talk-lags-em-currency-index</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于全球负面情绪对风险资产造成特别大的压力，且假期导致交易量持续清淡，新兴市场周一遭受重创。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/turkish-lira-slips-on-erdogan-rates-talk-lags-em-currency-index</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 09:07:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黄金上涨 26%，在金属市场涨跌互现的一年中脱颖而出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/gold-s-27-advance-stands-out-in-mixed-year-for-metals-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[黄金价格有望创造本世纪最大的年度涨幅之一，受美国货币宽松政策、持续的地缘政治风险以及各国央行的购买浪潮推动，黄金价格已上涨 26%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/gold-s-27-advance-stands-out-in-mixed-year-for-metals-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 04:09:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
